STEP 3 — TRIGGER LOGIC ENGINE

Determine what event should activate the order.

Possible triggers:

• Breakout

• Pullback

• Reclaim

• Liquidity Sweep

• Continuation

• Trend Resumption

• Volatility Expansion

Additional Trigger Conditions:

• Execution Survivability Confirmed

• Volatility Acceptable

• Spread Acceptable

• Execution Buffer Preserved

