STEP 5 — ORDER EXPIRATION ENGINE

Determine:

When should the order automatically become invalid?

Examples:

• after structural failure

• after regime change

• after excessive delay

• after major event

Cancel pending order if:

• Execution Survivability becomes Unsafe

• Stop Survivability becomes Unacceptable

• Risk Deployment withdrawn

• Portfolio Exposure exceeds limits

